RELEASE NOTES
=============

This is the release "1.9.0" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

See https://docs.phyglos.org/bandit for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES
=============

* Set TARGET default partitions to none
* Check for previous mounts when entering TARGET
* Lazy unmount /dev and /proc when leaving TARGET or BUILDER
* Allow raising TARGET on a directory instead of a partition


